s&nbsp;<br>\n11.&nbsp;Panama&nbsp;ASI&nbsp;inspection,&nbsp;CICA&nbsp;Survey,&nbsp;MLC&nbsp;Survey&nbsp;and&nbsp;certification&nbsp;<br>\n12.&nbsp;Panama&nbsp;ship&nbsp;registry,&nbsp;including&nbsp;registry&nbsp;certificate,&nbsp;MSMC,&nbsp;radio&nbsp;station&nbsp;license,&nbsp;annual&nbsp;tax&nbsp;receipt&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;certifications,&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;authorisation,&nbsp;Extension,&nbsp;Dispensation,&nbsp;Exemption,&nbsp;BCC,&nbsp;WRC,&nbsp;CSR,&nbsp;DMLC&nbsp;PART&nbsp;I,&nbsp;ISSC,&nbsp;DECLARATION&nbsp;OF&nbsp;CSO,&nbsp;DPA,&nbsp;COMPANY,&nbsp;CLC,&nbsp;BWMP&nbsp;PLAN,&nbsp;IBWMC&nbsp;etc&nbsp;<br>\n13.&nbsp;OMCS&nbsp;Classification&nbsp;survey&nbsp;and&nbsp;certification,&nbsp;including&nbsp;Class&nbsp;Entry,&nbsp;Initial&nbsp;Survey,&nbsp;Annual&nbsp;Survey,&nbsp;Intermediate&nbsp;Survey,&nbsp;Renewal&nbsp;Survey,&nbsp;Additional&nbsp;Survey&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;statutory&nbsp;certificates&nbsp;<br>\n14.&nbsp;Panama&nbsp;Casualty&nbsp;Investigation&nbsp;<br>\n15.&nbsp;Panama&nbsp;Crew&nbsp;licences&nbsp;application&nbsp;<br>\n16.&nbsp;Port&nbsp;Agency&nbsp;operation,&nbsp;Marine&nbsp;warranty&nbsp;survey,&nbsp;On/Off&nbsp;hire&nbsp;survey,&nbsp;Delivery&nbsp;and&nbsp;Re-delivery&nbsp;survey,&nbsp;others&nbsp;maritime&nbsp;one-stop&nbsp;services.</p>",
